<p>App.ly is a tool to help you manage your applications.</p> 

<p>Applying for colleges? Jobs? Scholarships? Internships? We've got you covered.</p> 

<p>Never miss an application deadline again.</p> 

<p>Here's how it works:</p>

<p>YOU choose the type of opportunity you're applying for (e.g. college, job, scholarship, internship, or other) and fill out our customized form with all the particulars including the application's website link, due date, and number of recommendations needed. You can add your own items to the form and fill in as little or as much as you wish!</p>

<p>WE send you SMS (text message) reminders to your mobile device letting you know you have an application due. You can choose to receive reminders 1 month, 2 weeks, 1 week, and 1 day before the application's due date.</p>

<p>Log-in to app.ly on your desktop or mobile device to view all your saved application due dates and information.</p>

<p>Why app.ly? Simple. Success occurs when opportunity meets preparation. Let us handle the prep work. Go get em' kid.</p> 
